data.description: Delightful, low maintenance, pool home with covered parking just minutes from Old Town Key West can be yours.  This 2 bedroom, 1 bath move-in ready concrete block home has a metal roof, recently renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances including a gas stove, tankless hot water heater, Central A/C, electric vehicle plug, Nest energy saving thermostat, tile floors and an expansive patio with gas grill hookup.  Come see what easy living in paradise is all about!
